{"url": "https://www.her.ie/celeb/fairytales-really-exist-paris-hilton-chris-zylka-engaged-381795", "text": "\u201cI have never felt so happy, safe and loved.\"\n\nHuge congratulations are in order!\n\nParis Hilton and actor Chris Zylka are officially engaged.\n\nThe couple were in Aspen, Colardo for a holiday ski trip when the actor popped the question over the weekend, her rep confirmed to People.\n\nThe heiress told the magazine:\n\n\u201cI am so excited to be engaged to the love of my life and my best friend. \u201cI have never felt so happy, safe and loved. \u201cHe is perfect for me in every way and showed me that fairytales really do exist!\u201d\n\nAccording to the publication, the couple were posing for a picture in the ski town when he got down on one knee.\n\nOn the emotional moment, the 36-year-old businesswoman said:\n\n\u201cI was so excited and surprised! I immediately said yes!\u201d\n\nThe pair first met at a party during Oscars season almost a decade ago, but lost touch and didn\u2019t end up reconnecting until two years ago.\n\nThey went public with their relationship on social media in February 2017 with a sweet Instagram photo.\n\n#BirthdaySelfie with my loves \u2728??????\u2728 A post shared by Paris Hilton (@parishilton) on Feb 18, 2017 at 7:39pm PST\n\nThe couple sparked engagement rumours earlier this week when she was spotted with a dazzling diamond ring while they were strolling around the ski town.\n\nThe Simple Life star recently paid tribute to her beau with a sweet Instagram post.\n\nShe wrote:\n\n\u201cNever in a million years did I think I would find someone so completely perfect for me. \u201cSomeone who would make me happier than I ever dreamed I could be. Someone that would touch my life so profoundly & give me a whole new reason to breathe. \u201cBut then I found you & realized that everything I anticipated you to be doesn\u2019t even compare to how incredibly amazing you are\u2026\u201d\n\nPhoto via Getty.", "images": ["https://